""SELECT `c`.`id`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`shift_id`, `s`.`id`, `s`.`description`, `s0`.`id`, `s0`.`end`, `s0`.`shift_id`, `s0`.`start`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`cycle_id`, `t0`.`year`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`, `t0`.`name`, `t0`.`teacher_id`
FROM `cycle` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `shift` AS `s` ON `c`.`shift_id` = `s`.`id`
LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`
    FROM `course` AS `c0`
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT `c1`.`course_id`, `c1`.`subject_id`, `s1`.`id`, `s1`.`name`, `s1`.`teacher_id`
        FROM `course_has_subjects` AS `c1`
        INNER JOIN `subject` AS `s1` ON `c1`.`subject_id` = `s1`.`id`
    ) AS `t` ON `c0`.`id` = `t`.`course_id`
) AS `t0` ON `c`.`id` = `t0`.`cycle_id`

""SELECT `c`.`id`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`shift_id`, `s`.`id`, `s`.`description`, `s0`.`id`, `s0`.`end`, `s0`.`shift_id`, `s0`.`start`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`cycle_id`, `t0`.`year`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`, `t0`.`name`, `t0`.`teacher_id`
FROM `cycle` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `shift` AS `s` ON `c`.`shift_id` = `s`.`id`
LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`

INNER JOIN `shift` AS `s` ON `c`.`shift_id` = `s`.`id`
LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`
    FROM `course` AS `c0`

        SELECT `c1`.`course_id`, `c1`.`subject_id`, `s1`.`id`, `s1`.`name`, `s1`.`teacher_id`
        FROM `course_has_subjects` AS `c1`
        INNER JOIN `subject` AS `s1` ON `c1`.`subject_id` = `s1`.`id`

) AS `t0` ON `c`.`id` = `t0`.`cycle_id`

""SELECT `c`.`id`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`shift_id`, `s`.`id`, `s`.`description`, `s0`.`id`, `s0`.`end`, `s0`.`shift_id`, `s0`.`start`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`cycle_id`, `t0`.`year`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`, `t0`.`name`, `t0`.`teacher_id`
FROM `cycle` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `shift` AS `s` ON `c`.`shift_id` = `s`.`id`
LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`
    FROM `course` AS `c0`
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT `c1`.`course_id`, `c1`.`subject_id`, `s1`.`id`, `s1`.`name`, `s1`.`teacher_id`
        FROM `course_has_subjects` AS `c1`
        INNER JOIN `subject` AS `s1` ON `c1`.`subject_id` = `s1`.`id`
    ) AS `t` ON `c0`.`id` = `t`.`course_id`
) AS `t0` ON `c`.`id` = `t0`.`cycle_id`
ORDER BY `c`.`name`, `c`.`id`, `s`.`id`, `s0`.`id`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`" (0723d8ff)

FROM `cycle` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `shift` AS `s` ON `c`.`shift_id` = `s`.`id`
LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`

    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`

LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`

""SELECT `c`.`id`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`shift_id`, `s`.`id`, `s`.`description`, `s0`.`id`, `s0`.`end`, `s0`.`shift_id`, `s0`.`start`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`cycle_id`, `t0`.`year`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`, `t0`.`name`, `t0`.`teacher_id`
FROM `cycle` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `shift` AS `s` ON `c`.`shift_id` = `s`.`id`
LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`
    FROM `course` AS `c0`
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT `c1`.`course_id`, `c1`.`subject_id`, `s1`.`id`, `s1`.`name`, `s1`.`teacher_id`
        FROM `course_has_subjects` AS `c1`
        INNER JOIN `subject` AS `s1` ON `c1`.`subject_id` = `s1`.`id`
    ) AS `t` ON `c0`.`id` = `t`.`course_id`
) AS `t0` ON `c`.`id` = `t0`.`cycle_id`
ORDER BY `c`.`name`, `c`.`id`, `s`.`id`, `s0`.`id`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`" (0723d8ff)

LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`

""SELECT `c`.`id`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`shift_id`, `s`.`id`, `s`.`description`, `s0`.`id`, `s0`.`end`, `s0`.`shift_id`, `s0`.`start`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`cycle_id`, `t0`.`year`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`, `t0`.`name`, `t0`.`teacher_id`
FROM `cycle` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `shift` AS `s` ON `c`.`shift_id` = `s`.`id`
LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`
    FROM `course` AS `c0`
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT `c1`.`course_id`, `c1`.`subject_id`, `s1`.`id`, `s1`.`name`, `s1`.`teacher_id`
        FROM `course_has_subjects` AS `c1`
        INNER JOIN `subject` AS `s1` ON `c1`.`subject_id` = `s1`.`id`
    ) AS `t` ON `c0`.`id` = `t`.`course_id`
) AS `t0` ON `c`.`id` = `t0`.`cycle_id`

""SELECT `c`.`id`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`shift_id`, `s`.`id`, `s`.`description`, `s0`.`id`, `s0`.`end`, `s0`.`shift_id`, `s0`.`start`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`cycle_id`, `t0`.`year`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`, `t0`.`name`, `t0`.`teacher_id`
FROM `cycle` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `shift` AS `s` ON `c`.`shift_id` = `s`.`id`
LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`
    FROM `course` AS `c0`
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT `c1`.`course_id`, `c1`.`subject_id`, `s1`.`id`, `s1`.`name`, `s1`.`teacher_id`
        FROM `course_has_subjects` AS `c1`
        INNER JOIN `subject` AS `s1` ON `c1`.`subject_id` = `s1`.`id`
    ) AS `t` ON `c0`.`id` = `t`.`course_id`
) AS `t0` ON `c`.`id` = `t0`.`cycle_id`

""SELECT `c`.`id`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`shift_id`, `s`.`id`, `s`.`description`, `s0`.`id`, `s0`.`end`, `s0`.`shift_id`, `s0`.`start`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`cycle_id`, `t0`.`year`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`, `t0`.`name`, `t0`.`teacher_id`
FROM `cycle` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `shift` AS `s` ON `c`.`shift_id` = `s`.`id`
LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`

""SELECT `c`.`id`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`shift_id`, `s`.`id`, `s`.`description`, `s0`.`id`, `s0`.`end`, `s0`.`shift_id`, `s0`.`start`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`cycle_id`, `t0`.`year`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`, `t0`.`name`, `t0`.`teacher_id`
FROM `cycle` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `shift` AS `s` ON `c`.`shift_id` = `s`.`id`
LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`

2020-04-27T21:33:40.2972116+02:00 0HLVAS6FVQ07P:00000002 [INF] Petición de listado de grados recibida (7cfff5cc)
2020-04-27T21:33:40.3015778+02:00 0HLVAS6FVQ07P:00000002 [INF] Entity Framework Core "3.1.0" initialized '"AttendanceControlDBContext"' using provider '"Pomelo.EntityFrameworkCore.MySql"' with options: "None" (9958f5bb)
2020-04-27T21:33:40.3134075+02:00 0HLVAS6FVQ07P:00000002 [INF] Executed DbCommand ("4"ms) [Parameters=[""], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT `c`.`id`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`shift_id`, `s`.`id`, `s`.`description`, `s0`.`id`, `s0`.`end`, `s0`.`shift_id`, `s0`.`start`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`cycle_id`, `t0`.`year`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`, `t0`.`name`, `t0`.`teacher_id`
FROM `cycle` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `shift` AS `s` ON `c`.`shift_id` = `s`.`id`
LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`
    FROM `course` AS `c0`
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT `c1`.`course_id`, `c1`.`subject_id`, `s1`.`id`, `s1`.`name`, `s1`.`teacher_id`
        FROM `course_has_subjects` AS `c1`
        INNER JOIN `subject` AS `s1` ON `c1`.`subject_id` = `s1`.`id`

""SELECT `c`.`id`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`shift_id`, `s`.`id`, `s`.`description`, `s0`.`id`, `s0`.`end`, `s0`.`shift_id`, `s0`.`start`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`cycle_id`, `t0`.`year`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`, `t0`.`name`, `t0`.`teacher_id`
FROM `cycle` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `shift` AS `s` ON `c`.`shift_id` = `s`.`id`
LEFT JOIN `schedule` AS `s0` ON `s`.`id` = `s0`.`shift_id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`
    FROM `course` AS `c0`

        SELECT `c1`.`course_id`, `c1`.`subject_id`, `s1`.`id`, `s1`.`name`, `s1`.`teacher_id`
        FROM `course_has_subjects` AS `c1`
        INNER JOIN `subject` AS `s1` ON `c1`.`subject_id` = `s1`.`id`

) AS `t0` ON `c`.`id` = `t0`.`cycle_id`
